OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,FThe UK's worst airports for flight
OL,7,Fdelays have been ranked following new
OL,8,Fanalysis of data released by the Civil
OL,9,FAviation Authority.
OL,11,FBournemouth Airport ranked third with
OL,12,Fflights delays averaging 17 minutes
OL,13,Fand 18 seconds.
OL,15,FSouthampton came in as the fourth
OL,16,Fworst for delays with an average of 16
OL,17,Fminutes and 36 seconds. While Gatwick
OL,18,Fwas fifth with delays averaging 16
OL,19,Fminutes and 24 seconds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
