OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,FElsewhere, Manchester Airport was
OL,7,Franked the worst acros the UK with an
OL,8,Faverage which topped at out at more
OL,9,Fthan nineteen minutes last year.
OL,10,FBirmingham Airport was close behind
OL,11,Fwith the second poorest flight
OL,12,Fpunctuality of 18 minutes and 42
OL,13,Fseconds.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Liverpool John Lennon
OL,16,FAirport had the most punctual flights,
OL,17,Frecording an average delay of just
OL,18,Fnine minutes and 24 seconds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
