OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,FA spokesman for Bournemouth Airport
OL,7,Fsaid the reason for delays are outside
OL,8,Fits control "in the majority of
OL,9,Fcases", and it is "one of the UK's top-
OL,10,Franked regional airports for passenger
OL,11,Fsatisfaction".
OL,13,FSouthampton Airport and Gatwick
OL,14,FAirport have been approached for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,17,FRory Boland, editor of magazine Which?
OL,18,FTravel, said the choice of airport
OL,19,F"shouldn't make or break your trip"
OL,20,Fbut "too many holidays got off to a
OL,21,Fterrible start last year".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,F"For passengers already wary of travel
OL,7,Funcertainty, seeing such consistent
OL,8,Funderperformance makes it difficult to
OL,9,Fbook with any real confidence."
OL,11,FThe analysis took into account
OL,12,Fscheduled and chartered departures
OL,13,Ffrom the 23 commercial UK airports
OL,14,Fwith at least 1,000 outbound flights
OL,15,Flast year. Cancellations were not
OL,16,Fincluded.
OL,18,FThe average delay for departures last
OL,19,Fyear was 14 minutes and 54 seconds,
OL,20,Fdown from 18 minutes and 24 seconds in
OL,21,F2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
