OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,FDepending on the distance of the route
OL,7,Fand length of delay, passengers booked
OL,8,Fon delayed flights from UK airports
OL,9,Fare entitled to assistance such as a
OL,10,Freasonable amount of food and drink, a
OL,11,Fmeans to communicate and overnight
OL,12,Faccommodation if required.
OL,14,FPassengers may also be able to claim
OL,15,Fcompensation of up to #520 from the
OL,16,Fairline if the reason for the delay is
OL,17,Fdeemed within its control, which could
OL,18,Fbe a fault with the aircraft or pilot
OL,19,Fsickness.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,FAir Traffic Control issues are
OL,7,Fconsidered to be an "extraordinary
OL,8,Fcircumstance", meaning affected
OL,9,Fpassengers are not entitled to payouts.
OL,11,FAnna Bowles, head of consumer at the
OL,12,FCAA, urged the aviation industry to be
OL,13,F"focused on delivering punctual and
OL,14,Freliable journeys for passengers
OL,15,Fwherever possible" as she warned that
OL,16,Fdelays have a "real impact for people
OL,17,Fheading off on holidays".
OL,19,FShe added: "When disruption occurs,
OL,20,Fhow the industry responds really
OL,21,Fmatters.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777964751
OL,3,CThree of South's airports among worst
OL,4,Cin UK for delays
OL,6,F"Passengers should be kept informed
OL,7,Fand given the care and support they
OL,8,Fare entitled to."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for trade body
OL,11,FAirportsUK said passengers are
OL,12,F"benefitting from improvements in the
OL,13,Fservice they receive", and delays in
OL,14,F2025 were "down significantly on the
OL,15,Fprevious year".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
